# Project Architecture

## System Overview
Full-stack TypeScript monorepo: Node.js backend + React frontend + shared types + real-time WebSocket.

## Backend (`/server/`)
- `index.ts` - Express server entry point
- `routes/` - API route handlers
- `websocket/` - WebSocket server manager
- `database/` - Prisma connection management
- `middleware/` - Express middleware (ingress, request logging)
- `utils/` - Utilities (structured logger)
- `prisma/` - Prisma schema and migrations

## Frontend (`/client/`)
- `src/App.tsx` - Root application component
- `src/pages/` - Page components (one per feature/tab)
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `src/hooks/` - Custom React hooks (WebSocket, localStorage, API)
- `src/services/` - API client (axios)
- `src/styles/` - Shared CSS
- `src/modals/` - Modal components
- `src/layouts/` - Layout components
- `src/utils/` - Utility functions

## Shared Types (`/types/`)
- `index.ts` - TypeScript interfaces shared between client and server

## Infrastructure
- `config.yaml` - HA add-on configuration
- `Dockerfile` - Multi-stage Docker build
- `build.yaml` - Multi-arch build targets
- `run.sh` - HA startup script
- `docker-compose.yml` - Local PostgreSQL for development
- `pnpm-workspace.yaml` - Workspace definition

## Import Aliases (Client)
- `@components/*`, `@pages/*`, `@hooks/*`, `@services/*`, `@layouts/*`, `@modals/*`, `@utils/*`, `@styles/*`
